comments: Ann Marie is a brilliant and interesting woman who is not at all "woo-woo" (as they say).

Anne-Marie Oliver is truly a great teacher and thinker. She allows students to look at the world in a different way through her readings,personality,and generosity. She will be an excellent educator for years to come and would boost the academic reputation for any major institution.
SHE IS BRILLIANT!!!!!!!! I love Anne-Marie!

I\'ve had 2 classes with her and found them to be the most challenging classes ever attended and surprisingly did the best as well.Anne Marie is by far one of my highest influences in my life.She is such an amazing woman and parent!!!And read her book

Anne Marie Oliver always keeps it interesting in the classroom. She is extremely generous with her time and feedback. Her criticality and dedication with her subject matter is amazing and she always supports and backs up her students. She will make you think about things in a new way, demand a lot (of reading), and probably make you laugh too.
